le Watching) 现场都柏林 2/12/24" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/yVtIdhPsQ2U?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Sam Fender - Arms Length - 未发行现场首秀 - Dublin 3Arena" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/95cI2L98qk8?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">上帝保佑萨姆芬德<a href="https://t.co/SeQmSkpC5t">pic.twitter.com/SeQmSkpC5t</a></p><p> -拉娜౨ৎ（@drvnkrunn1ng） <a href="https://twitter.com/drvnkrunn1ng/status/1863761575053529239?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024年12月3日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">萨姆芬德你拥有我的心<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f972.png" alt="🥲" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://t.co/AGEgfCdBmE">pic.twitter.com/AGEgfCdBmE</a></p><p> — 凯莎<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f680.png" alt="🚀" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/2754.png" alt="❔" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> ||遇见雅各布·斯莱特？？？ (@_bl0ndieskeetz) <a href="https://twitter.com/_bl0ndieskeetz/status/1863758065113153725?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 12 月 3 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-widt